SUMMARY:Easter at Sonoma County Fairgrounds
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Easter at the Sonoma County Fairgrounds in Santa Rosa with a fun-filled\, family-friendly event for all ages. Enjoy two Easter services\, 9:00 AM and 11:00 AM\, and indoor egg hunts throughout the morning\, ensuring every child has a chance to participate and take home a candy bag.    The day features local food trucks\, free coffee\, and professional family photos\, along with kids’ activities including a bunny petting zoo\, secure play areas\, and a dedicated safety team.    Bring your family and friends to experience a joyful Easter celebration in a welcoming and safe environment\, with plenty of opportunities to connect\, play\, and create lasting memories together.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/easter-at-sonoma-county-fairgrounds/
LOCATION:1450 Bennett Valley Rd, , Santa Rosa, CA, 95404, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Dining,Family Friendly,Food,Holiday,Outdoors,Sonoma County
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/03/13230131/6e59dcca-df5a-478b-849a-4bf70af39985-imported-asset__postcard.png
END:VEVENT
