SUMMARY:Sebastopol Documentary Film Festival Closing PARTY
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the finale of the Sebastopol Documentary Film Festival with a special closing night party and screening of Peter Asher: Everywhere Man. Held at the Robert Brent Auditorium inside the Sebastopol Center for the Arts\, this event brings the festival to a memorable close with film\, community\, and celebration.    Guests will enjoy an engaging screening followed by a lively atmosphere perfect for connecting with fellow film lovers and creatives.     General admission tickets are available\, offering access to both the film and the closing festivities. Don’t miss this opportunity to wrap up the festival with an inspiring documentary and an evening of art\, culture\, and connection.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/sebastopol-documentary-film-festival-closing-party/
LOCATION:282 South High Street, Sebastopol, CA, 95472, United States
GEO:-122.825271;38.400121
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Fairs & Festivals,Film,Sonoma County
