SUMMARY:Bohemian Highway at The California Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Experience a night of Americana and folk rock at The California Theatre with Bohemian Highway\, a six-piece band known for rich harmonies and danceable melodies. Led by Doug Blumer\, their original songs celebrate nature\, love\, and shared experiences. Opening the evening is the Callie Watts Band\, performing Callie’s original music with a talented ensemble of musicians.    Together\, these acts promise a lively and heartfelt night of music\, showcasing the best of Sonoma County’s vibrant music scene.      Join for an unforgettable evening of original songwriting\, engaging performances\, and the warm energy of live music.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/bohemian-highway-at-the-california-theatre/
LOCATION:528 7th Street, Santa Rosa, CA, 95401, United States
CATEGORIES:Live Music,Music,Performing Arts,Sonoma County
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/04/05002002/meta_eyJzcmNCdWNrZXQiOiJiemdsZmlsZXMifQ-7.png
